{
  "texts": [
    "Although CCAM-Person demonstrates excellent performance on most metrics, it does not reach the optimal inference speed.",
    "We attribute this to the inclusion of the attention mechanism and the complex interaction of feature information, which often come with complex structures and larger parameter sizes, leading to decreased runtime efficiency.",
    "While our efficiency is not at the highest level, it remains capable of fulfilling the real-time demands of a majority of tasks.",
    "Our work proposes a framework called CCAM-Person for person detection and pose estimation.",
    "Comparative experiments on large-scale public datasets with other real-time human pose estimation methods demonstrate competitive results in terms of regression accuracy and inference speed."
  ]
}